Malice:

As more opponents showed up, malice could only grin.  Since Trelos was turning fast enough to keep from being outflanked, He ignited his flight engines and flew up to avoid the missile.  He fired into the hardened lava under his enemies&#39; feet, then fired a flurry of grenades into the weakened ground.  He then transformed into the waverider craft, proudly showing his Decepticon insignias on his wings, then flew straight down.  He transformed at the last minute to land on his feet.  His momentum caused the weakened slab of rock to tilt up.  The fresh lava that flowed up to him was no concern, as he drew the thermal energy into his body, leaving his air frame safe.

&quot;Words are a sign of stupidity, you bunch of punk children.  You all talk a bit too much,&quot; Malice retorted, breaking free after his short break to fly low to the ground toward the base&#39;s entrance.

OOC:  The three sent to take care of malice are far from any danger of getting hurt.  Its more to sting their pride.  he&#39;s just there to stir up trouble.


