As the Predacon base rose to the surface Myrmidon was close behind
Trelos. He took a moment to look around as he carefully stepped onto
the the cooling surface, steam rising from the contact. With the
slightest application of power, bosters flared and he rose above the
muck. 

He watched as Trelos ran at the new robot and watched the result, a
slight smile flitting across his face. With a flick of thought he began
transmitting what he saw to the command center, as he began to approach
Malice. (OOC: Yes, Hydras should be able to see what&#39;s going on)

&quot;Who are you to invade our space with threats of death?&quot; His voice is
deep, a cross between a purr and a growl. Shouldermounted motar cannons
turned to orient on the necommer as he continued, &quot;It is you who will
stand down, and you will do it *now*&quot;

Preston
